knimeNode.name: FSK to R (Kotlin)
knimeNode.shortDescription: Extracts the R workspace out of an FSK object. The R workspace may be used with KNIME R nodes.

fullDescription.intro: Extracts the R workspace out of an FSK object and places it into the output RPortObject. If the R workspace is null or non-existent (as when the model has not been run), the generated RPortObject would be null.
